T1  - Exporting raises productivity in sub-Saharan African manufacturing firms
AU  - Van Biesebroeck, Johannes
JO  - Journal of International Economics
VL  - 67
IS  - 2
SP  - 373
EP  - 391
PY  - 2005
DA  - 2005/12/01/
